  m_text: "\rConstance rushes forward again, the life around her slowly decaying,
    suddenly people are screaming, crying, disappearing into dust. \n\nThe world
    begins to crumble, colors bleeding into each other, faces melting into one another.\r\n\nConstance
    breaks out into a run, an exit, there has to be an exit somewhere! \n\r"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
